Package org.testfx.service.support

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Capture
    Essentially a Supplier that returns an Image via Capture.getImage()
    CaptureSupport  
    PixelMatcher  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FiredEvents
    Stores a list of events that have been fired since the start of a test; useful for debugging.
    PixelMatcherResult
    Indicates how similar/dissimilar two images were on a pixel-to-pixel comparison level via PixelMatcher.match(Image, Image).
    WaitUntilSupport
    Provides methods that will wait for a given node or value to meet a given condition by repeatedly testing that item until the condition is met or the timeout is reached.
